When I purchased this, my pause was whether the Dirty Dancing film on this was the Patrick Swayze/Jennifer Grey version, or some other film package by same title.  The product description and reviews to date didn't make clear.  So I thought I'd post here to affirm to others that it is indeed  Patrick Swayze/Jennifer Grey film.
